message.content: cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.BIO, cs.AI, cs.NEURON - The paper proposes a machine learning approach using deep neural networks to correct for Mie scattering in Fourier transformed infrared spectra of biological samples. This involves image processing techniques (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NEURON) applied to biological data (cs.BIO).
